arStrings.szText: You deal {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0" / Affix."Static Value 2" * 100|x%|]{/c} increased Burning damage to enemies for each second they remain Burning, up to {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0" * 100|x%|]{/c} after {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 2"]{/c} seconds. Additionally, you deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased Burning damage to enemies that are not {c_important}{u}Healthy{/u}{/c}.

You deal {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0" / Affix."Static Value 2" * 100|x%|]{/c} increased Burning damage to enemies for each second they remain Burning and {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased Burning damage to injured enemies.
